CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 17, 1961, pg. 6A reads: "Grand Master Speaks - The Hon. Samuel T. Daniels, Grand Master of the Most Worshipful Prince Hall Grand Lodge of Maryland, gave a stirring address at the banquet held by the Grand Lodge, in Pittsburgh, recently."
TitMainTitle: Group of eight men, all wearing tuxedos, some wearing ribbons with Masonic emblem, standing outside the Penn Sheraton hotel below marquee inscribed "Welcome Grand Lodge Masons"
